{| style="text-align: left; width: 30%" border="0" |- |(18)||''wesra''|| ''nos''||''na-in-tha-te'' |- | ||Guanay|| far||be-NEG-DIM-DCL |- | || colspan=3 |‘Guanay is very near.’ |}
